00:35:22.520 --> 00:35:24.920
to make a decision
as to how much risk

00:35:24.920 --> 00:35:26.890
you are willing to take.

00:35:26.890 --> 00:35:29.080
And then, based on
that, the lower the risk

00:35:29.080 --> 00:35:33.520
you can take the higher, you
have to raise your elevation.

00:35:33.520 --> 00:35:38.110
