00:40:03.410 --> 00:40:04.910
Because it was just Boston.

00:40:04.910 --> 00:40:07.652
And I live in Cambridge,
and there's Arlington,

00:40:07.652 --> 00:40:09.360
and there's Somerville,
and there are all

00:40:09.360 --> 00:40:10.790
these different communities.

00:40:10.790 --> 00:40:14.580
So where's the conversation
about having us really

00:40:14.580 --> 00:40:15.850
be coordinated?

00:40:15.850 --> 00:40:18.040
It looks like we're,
as you said, coming up

00:40:18.040 --> 00:40:20.600
with the end of figuring out
where the water will go if it's

00:40:20.600 --> 00:40:22.430
just left, if we do nothing?

00:40:22.430 --> 00:40:26.069
But who's coordinating all this
activity of and great research

00:40:26.069 --> 00:40:27.110
and entering into action?

00:40:27.110 --> 00:40:30.220
- That's a very good question.

00:40:30.220 --> 00:40:33.290
You know, so,
miss, I've actually

00:40:33.290 --> 00:40:35.240
been thinking about
this question a lot.

00:40:35.240 --> 00:40:39.170
Because as a hydrologist, I
think about storm water a lot,

00:40:39.170 --> 00:40:40.440
with extreme precipitation.

00:40:40.440 --> 00:40:43.250
And every town is responsible
for their own storm water

00:40:43.250 --> 00:40:43.970
management.

00:40:43.970 --> 00:40:47.290
Wouldn't it make sense if all
the towns got together and came

00:40:47.290 --> 00:40:50.980
up with a plan that worked
so that everybody could sort

00:40:50.980 --> 00:40:53.460
of take advantage of the
information others had

00:40:53.460 --> 00:40:54.750
that all makes logical sense?

00:40:54.750 --> 00:40:57.780
And actually, when it
comes to the adaptation

00:40:57.780 --> 00:41:00.350
for coastal flooding,
that's beginning to happen.

00:41:00.350 --> 00:41:03.260
So because the flooding
is so extensive

00:41:03.260 --> 00:41:06.610
and it gets worse
over time, people

00:41:06.610 --> 00:41:08.700
within city of Boston and
surrounding communities

00:41:08.700 --> 00:41:09.950
are starting to work together.

00:41:09.950 --> 00:41:11.780
There's this-- I forget
what it's called,

00:41:11.780 --> 00:41:14.970
but there's a group of mayors
in Boston and surrounding

00:41:14.970 --> 00:41:15.860
communities.

00:41:15.860 --> 00:41:17.270
It's called the Mayor's
Summit or something like that.

00:41:17.270 --> 00:41:19.300
I should know the answer
to the name of that.

00:41:19.300 --> 00:41:20.900
But anyway, they've
gotten together

00:41:20.900 --> 00:41:23.850
